            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-264] docs should include a state transition diagram for client state</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-264</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;we should have a state transition diagram to help users understand client state transitions. perhaps the edges could indicate what might cause such a  transition? (not sure if that will work). keep in mind for the states that the java/c clients have diff names for constants (not sure how to handle). This should be added to the programmer guide in the appropriate section.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
